An '''[[atmosphere]]''' is a gas layer around a celestial body.

'''Atmosphere''' may also refer to:
* [[Atmosphere (unit)]], a unit of pressure
* [[Atmosphere of Earth]]
* [[Extraterrestrial atmospheres]]
* [[Stellar atmosphere]]

